description	"Din Djarin

Class: Arc Trooper.
Class Summary: 
A tanky hybrid melee/gunner with a double-damage sniper and a flamethrower. 

Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (3)
- Amban Phase-Pulse Blaster *
- The Darksaber *
- Wrist Flamethrower

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- Amban Phase-Pulse Blaster
- Based on Projectile Rifle
- Ignites enemies on successful hits

--- The Darksaber
- Defense (1)
- Can use Yellow, Red and Purple styles
- Cannot block blaster fire
- Can block lightsabers 
- Cannot slap

Attributes:
- Fuel (3)
- Regenerating Fuel
- Cortosis
- Magnetic Plating
- Blast Armor
- Shield Regeneration (1)

Abilities:
- Stamina (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dexterity (1) [Alt Ability 1]

With his Mandalorian armor and distinctive beskar helmet, Djarin was both well-equipped and enigmatic, a stranger whose past was shrouded in mystery to others."